      "contentFieldValue": {
        "data": "<h2 data-end=\"97\" data-start=\"45\"><strong data-end=\"63\" data-start=\"45\">Incident Date:</strong> February 5th, 2026 at 18:00 UTC</h2>\n\n<p data-end=\"178\" data-start=\"99\">&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p data-end=\"178\" data-start=\"99\">During the affected period, customers may have experienced data unavailability or inconsistencies within Analytics Cloud. In some cases, this resulted in partial data unavailability, while in others, customers may have experienced near-complete data unavailability for the duration of the incident. This could have impacted data visibility and accuracy across reports and dashboards.</p>\n\n<p data-end=\"681\" data-start=\"565\">The incident has been identified and addressed, and Analytics Cloud is now operating normally with data processing resumed.&nbsp;We apologize for any inconvenience caused and appreciate your understanding.</p>"
      },
